            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"out-of-the-smoke\">Out of the Smoke</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Access to clean fuels and technologies for cooking (% of population) from 2000 to 2023 for 12 countries. India's transformation from 23% to 77% stands out. Indonesia leapt from 7% to 91%. Ethiopia barely reached 7%.</span></span>"
